{"tid":999934,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"珠海市委書記：爭取港澳車不用其他牌照可到珠海","createTime":"2019-01-29T05:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T06:23:13.000Z","uid":127569,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b9cab6b3162323a79ef6381e8c2ad8d7b9f096ef","tid":999934,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/story/566d0ade6db28c273c000001/5c4f0f1be603836110bf3d41/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fstory%2F566d0ade6db28c273c000001%2F5c4f0f1be603836110bf3d41%2F&d=Osx8LrH6dWr2xFCVFeSzB9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=8f8b4c9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/story/566d0ade6db28c273c000001/5c4f0f1be603836110bf3d41/</a><br />\n<br />\n珠海市委書記郭永航表示：「修橋幹甚麼？修橋就是為了就走車，最終肯定是要放寬，但是可能目前會有一些現實的制約條件。」被問到主要制約是甚麼時，郭永航稱：「問香港政府。」<br />\n<br />\n郭永航出席珠海市代表團全體會議，指將來會爭取香港和澳門車輛毋須申請其他車牌，便可通過港珠澳大橋前往珠海；又指珠江東岸城市，包括香港和深圳相當發達，珠江西岸的珠海和澳門發展相對不足。"},{"pid":"55eda46ecc7eacfbc349c4f35c4ab01336551844","tid":999934,"uid":127569,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"又想破壞一國兩制，左右軚不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5d6da32e775d94bbeded2ce8e59d898e04d3d8","tid":999934,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"班王牛少咗好多生意. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17caba784624be8ad8088be30abfa1d38bc6a61","tid":999934,"uid":6532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"爭取埋粵C進入港澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e620c9e4e456e5367480fef9a4855b21e18cb5","tid":999934,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"記者問佢有咩制約條件，條支那官仲要串柒香港，叫記者問香港政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.